snippet.title: Timon & Pumbaa's Jungle Games (Windows game 1995)
snippet.description:
Timon and Pumbaa's Jungle is a party game based on Timon & Pumbaa of Walt Disney Television.
It offers five games such as Burper, Jungle Pinball, Sling Shooter, Bug Drop, Hippo Hop.
It's also released for Nintendo Super NES (1997).
